name: "Peace n Philly Shirts"
description:
"Peace N Philly shirts" were created to promote love & peace throughout Philadelphia & the world.

"Peace N Philly Shirts" were initally created in 2007 when Philadelphia was top 3 in the nation for murders. We're now reintroducing the shirts to help benefit a close Friend, son, brother, & father by the Name of Maurice Kimble who was murdered. He left behind his Loving son Mahki who he love dearly. The Profits from the 1st 100 shirts sold will benfit Mahki & Maurices Family. Can you help??

Allow 7-10 days for shipping
